snippet.title: Last Expedition | Transmission
snippet.description:
From an unknown galaxy, a long-range recon probe has sent a transmission... 

Last Expedition is a web3 PvPvE extraction FPS driven by action, suspense and a hazardous alien planet where everything wants to annihilate you.
